<p>Thank you for your reservation, {{name}} !</p>

<p>Here are your reservation details:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Confirmation code:</strong> {{confirmationCode}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Room:</strong> {{roomLabel}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Check-in:</strong> {{formatDate checkIn}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Check-out:</strong> {{formatDate checkOut}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Number of nights:</strong> {{nights}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>Number of guests:</strong> {{guests}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Rate per night:</strong> {{money nightlyPrice}}</p>
</div>

<p><strong>Price details:</strong></p>

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
  <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid #333;">
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Subtotal</td>
    <td style="text-align: right; padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">{{money subtotal}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <td style="padding: 8px;">Lodging tax (3.5%)</td>
    <td style="text-align: right; padding: 8px;">{{money accommodationTax}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <td style="padding: 8px;">GST (5%)</td>
    <td style="text-align: right; padding: 8px;">{{money tps}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 2px solid #333;">
    <td style="padding: 8px;">QST (9.975%)</td>
    <td style="text-align: right; padding: 8px;">{{money tvq}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">Total (taxes included)</td>
    <td style="text-align: right; padding: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">{{money total}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="color: #45464d; font-size: 13px;">Applicable taxes (lodging tax, GST and QST) are included in the total above.</p>

<p>You can manage your reservation by clicking the link below:</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
  <a href="{{manageUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background-color: #9d4300; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">Manage my reservation</a>
</p>

<p>We look forward to welcoming you!</p>

<p>Best regards,<br/>
The Vieux Pont team</p>
